ny among many sports sponsorships molson andor coors also have deals with the montreal canadiens ottawa senators toronto maple leafs edmonton oilers colorado avalanche arizona coyotes and detroit red wings and their beverages can be purchased at other sports venues such as the home of the philadelphia flyers the wells fargo center the washington capitals at the verizon center and bridgestone arena home of the nashville predators brandsedit main article molson coors brands molson brands include carling black label and molson canadian galleryedit molson family brewery after the fire of  molson dry bottles in refrigerator molson export beer bottle label other venturesedit main article molson family outside of beer and ice hockey the molson family were pioneers in steamships hospitality assisting with the building of the montreal hospital patrons of the arts and until  involved in banking too through molson bank which merged with the bank of montreal molson was once the owner of home improvement chains beaver lumber and aikenheads home improvement warehouse in february  molson sold  interest in aikenheads to home depot inc for  million  and later beaver lumber to home hardware in  see alsoedit beer portal companies portal canada portal canadian beer labatt list of breweries in canada ken westerfield molson frisbee team referencesedit  beer brewing  drinking beer molson coors retrieved    jaekyoung kim  centennial firms dry up in korea korea times retrieved    httpwwwtheglobeandmailcomreportonbusinessmolsoncoorssettleslawsuitwithmilleroverbranddistributionincanadaarticle  molson internal publications  molson coors completes acquisition of full ownership of millercoors and global miller brand portfolio molsoncoorscom october   retrieved january   becomes world’s third largest brewer by enterprise value and strengthens position in highly attractive us beer market   cbcca cbcca  retrieved   external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to molson breweries official 